  "text": "To obtain the relativistic restricted three-body problem equations of motion, the components of the metric tensor were calculated using the post-Newtonian approximation as described by Weinberg [CITATION_1] (with the exception that they are derived in proper time and not coordinate time). The metric tensor components in a co-rotating frame are",
